Sentencas: High ion conducting room temperature stabilized gamma-Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 has been successfully synthesized in thin film form on glass and alumina substrates.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The films were characterized for their structural properties like XRD, SEM, EDAX and AFM. Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 films deposited on alumina substrate showed single-phase nature with tetragonal crystal structure.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The AFM study reveals the considerable change in growth morphology on alumina substrate.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The temperature dependent ionic conductivity of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 films synthesized on glass and alumina substrates were studied using impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: The high ionic conductivity has been observed at lower temperature for Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 thin films synthesized on alumina substrates.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films

Sentencas: With these comparisons, alumina substrate proves its candidature for deposition of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 films for solid oxide fuel cell applications.
Titulo: Substrate dependent structural and electrical properties of Bi2Cu0.1V0.9O5.35 solid electrolyte thin films
